text:
Hey @UPS @UPSHelp you may want to tell your crew to close up that back door, oh and a few deliveries won’t be making it!

Our @WNCN news team just had multiple boxes flying at us on I-440W just before the Six Forks exit.

Tried to get driver’s attention to no avail. #SafetyFirst https://t.co/OPCmPAZbeA

@newsladyB Thank you for taking the time to alert our team about this. We want to ensure we have as many details as possible to have this taken care of. If your team is able to provide any additional details such as truck/plate number further location details. Please DM to let us know. ^AS https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
